  "Clear EEPROM when update SW": {
   "width": 14940,
   "height": 10140,
   "color": "rgb(255,255,225)",
   "labels": [
    {
     "text": "Clear EEPROM after replacing TCU or CVT assembly/ SW update",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2520,
      "top": 120,
      "height": 552,
      "width": 10800
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "",
      "size": 18.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "A.TCU is replaced with used unit or CVT assembly is replaced with new or used unit",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 1560,
      "top": 960,
      "height": 480,
      "width": 13320
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@Arial Unicode MS",
      "size": 12.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 1. Turn the ignition swtich \"ON\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 2250,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 9960
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 4. Please brake pedal and accelerator pedal",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 8700,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 3. Click the  button while depressing the brake pedal with the left foot and the accelerator pedal slightly with the right foot (accelerator pedal angle : approximately 2/8)",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,255)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 3150,
      "height": 840,
      "width": 11280
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 2. Shift the selector lever to \"R\" position",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 2700,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 7560
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 5. Turn the ignition switch \"OFF\" and hold it for 10 seconds or more ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 9150,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 12360
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": " 6. Turn the ignition switch \"ON\" ",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 9600,
      "height": 420,
      "width": 9600
     },
     "font": {
      "name": "@?? ??",
      "size": 10.0,
      "bold": "1",
      "italic": "0"
     }
    },
    {
     "text": "    Then you can see that 6 monitoring values in the list below are immediately changed to \"0\"",
     "color": "rgb(255,255,255)",
     "alignment": "0",
     "fontcolor": "rgb(0,0,0)",
     "bbox": {
      "left": 2280,
      "top": 4650,
